  "title": "Programme Coordinator | Nursing Home",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Assist in planning and coordinating monthly activities for seniors</li>\n  <li>Collect evaluation, feebacks on activities</li>\n  <li>Assist with seniors enquireies and provide information and referrals</li>\n  <li>Ensure equipment and supplies are sufficient</li>\n  <li>Assist to procure materials for activity, equipment and supplies when require</li>\n  <li>Support Program Executive in budget management and maintain program databases.</li>\n  <li>Perform general administrative tasks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level or Certificate in Community &amp; Social Services</li>\n  <li>Experience working with seniors preferred.</li>\n  <li>Working hours: 5.5days </li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Check out http://abercare.sg/jobs-vacancies/ for details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicant please email your detailed resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
